                                                                                                          '                `"WORKSPACE"`.\n'
                                                                                                          '              example:\n'
                                                                                                          '              - WORKSPACE\n'
                                                                                                          '              items:\n'

                                                                                                          '                - ORGANIZATION\n'
                                                                                                          '                - MANAGEMENT_GROUP\n'

                                                                                                          '            displayName:\n'
                                                                                                          '              description: Brief name for this resource type. If present, the UI may show\n'

                                                                                                          '              type: string\n'

                                                                                                          '              example: 1\n'

                                                                                                          '              readOnly: true\n'

                                                                                                          '              readOnly: true\n'
                                                                                                          '              type: string\n'
                                                                                                          '            singleInstance:\n'
                                                                                                          '              description: Single instance resources are static, non-instantiable and\n'
                                                                                                          '                do not use a `{uuid}`. They may represent service features or top-level\n'
                                                                                                          '                resources that always exist.\n'
                                                                                                          '              example: false\n'
                                                                                                          '              type: boolean\n'
                                                                                                          '            slug:\n'
                                                                                                          '              description: Must start with the provider identifier, followed by the actual\n'
